ity play also carries regulatory risk.", "date": "2026-07-17", "source": "Sportico", "tier": "T2", "url": "https://www.sportico.com/leagues/tennis/2026/aryna-sabalenka-jannik-sinner-luxury-accessories-gucci-1234901282/"}, {"name": "Lee Know (Stray Kids)", "act": "K팝 아이돌 (Stray Kids 멤버)", "brand": "Gucci", "role": "global ambassador", "region_focus": "NEA", "what_ko": "구찌가 스트레이 키즈 멤버 리노를 새 글로벌 브랜드 앰버서더로 발탁했다고 발표했다(기존 발탁, 지속 활동 중인 앰버서더로 재확인).", "what_en": "Gucci named Stray Kids member Lee Know as a Global Brand Ambassador, an existing appointment reconfirmed as an active ambassador relationship in the brand's current NEA roster.", "impact_ko": "발탁 발표 자체는 이전 시점의 뉴스이며, 이번 검색 기간 중 신규 활동(공연·룩 노출) 보도는 확인되지 않았다.", "impact_en": "The appointment itself predates this reporting window; no new activity (performance, look reveal) specific to this period was confirmed in current searches.", "date": "2025-06", "source": "WWD", "tier": "T1", "url": "https://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/gucci-stray-kids-member-lee-know-global-brand-ambassador-1237955449/"}], "has_data": true}